  "page": 158,
  "spans": [
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0002",
      "text": " 139",
      "bbox": [
        518.28,
        723.59,
        537.71,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0003",
      "text": "6.3.2",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        118.23,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0004",
      "text": "Explicit N_Port Login",
      "bbox": [
        128.24,
        57.65,
        229.3,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0005",
      "text": "6.3.2.1  Introduction",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        82.97,
        190.41,
        94.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0006",
      "text": "The explicit N_Port Login procedure shall require an Nx_Port to transmit a PLOGI Link request Se-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        106.97,
        539.97,
        118.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0007",
      "text": "quence. ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        118.97,
        134.35,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0008",
      "text": "Explicit N_Port Login replaces previous Service Parameters. The Login procedure shall follow the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        142.96,
        539.89,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0009",
      "text": "Exchange and Sequence management rules, the buffer-to-buffer flow control rules, and the end-to-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        154.96,
        539.85,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0010",
      "text": "end flow control rules as specified in FC-FS-2.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        166.96,
        300.4,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0011",
      "text": "A well-behaved Nx_Port shall Logout with another Nx_Port prior to initiating a new N_Port Login.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        190.96,
        540.02,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0012",
      "text": "However, if an Nx_Port receives or transmits a PLOGI request with another Nx_Port, it shall abnor-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        202.96,
        539.99,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0013",
      "text": "mally terminate open Sequences and respond to any new Sequences with that Nx_Port as though a",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        214.96,
        539.96,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0014",
      "text": "Logout had been previously performed.  During the N_Port Login procedure, other communication",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        226.96,
        539.94,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0015",
      "text": "with the destination Nx_Port shall not be initiated or accepted.  Once the N_Port Login procedure has",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        238.96,
        540.04,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0016",
      "text": "been successfully completed, communication between the Nx_Ports may be initiated or accepted,",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        250.96,
        539.97,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0017",
      "text": "(e.g., if Nx_Port(A) performs a PLOGI request with Nx_Port(B) and Nx_Port(B) transmits the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        262.96,
        540.0,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0018",
      "text": "LS_ACC reply, then either Nx_Port(A) or Nx_Port(B) may initiate communication for other protocols.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        274.96,
        540.03,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 8,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0019",
      "text": "Nx_Port(B) shall not be required to transmit a PLOGI request Sequence to Nx_Port(A) unless it wish-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        286.96,
        540.06,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 9,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0020",
      "text": "es to invalidate or alter the existing Login parameters).",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        298.96,
        336.44,
        310.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 10,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0021",
      "text": "6.3.2.2  N_Port Login - Fabric present",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        322.96,
        272.55,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0022",
      "text": "The destination Nx_Port explicit Login procedure requires transmission of a N_Port Login (PLOGI)",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        346.96,
        540.03,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0023",
      "text": "Link Service Sequence.  The PLOGI is sent within an Exchange with an assigned OX_ID, the D_ID of",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        358.96,
        540.06,
        370.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0024",
      "text": "the destination Nx_Port and a S_ID of originating Nx_Port.  The Payload of this Sequence contains",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        370.96,
        539.98,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0025",
      "text": "the Service Parameters, N_Port_Name, and Node_Name of the Nx_Port originating the PLOGI Se-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        382.96,
        539.95,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0026",
      "text": "quence.  The N_Port Service Parameters are as specified  in 6.6.  The applicability of the Service Pa-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        394.96,
        540.06,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0027",
      "text": "rameters to N_Port Login are given in tables 150 and 155.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        406.96,
        352.58,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0028",
      "text": "The normal reply Sequence to a PLOGI Link Service Sequence by an Nx_Port is a LS_ACC Link",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        430.96,
        539.97,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0029",
      "text": "Service Reply Sequence within the Exchange identified by the OX_ID of the Login Sequence and the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        442.96,
        539.99,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0030",
      "text": "RX_ID assigned by the Responder with a D_ID of the originating Nx_Port (PLOGI Sequence) and a",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.96,
        539.97,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0031",
      "text": "S_ID of the responding Nx_Port.  The Payload of the LS_ACC contains the Service Parameters of",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        466.96,
        540.04,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0032",
      "text": "the responding Nx_Port.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        478.96,
        203.75,
        490.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0033",
      "text": "6.3.2.3  Responses to N_Port Login - Fabric present",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.96,
        340.95,
        514.07
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0034",
      "text": "The following are possible responses the Nx_Port may receive in response to transmitting a PLOGI",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        526.96,
        539.99,
        538.07
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0035",
      "text": "with a Fabric present:",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        538.96,
        191.54,
        550.07
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0036",
      "text": "a) LS_ACC reply Sequence with OX_ID equal to the OX_ID of the PLOGI, and the Common Ser-",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        562.96,
        540.1,
        574.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0037",
      "text": "vice N_Port/F_Port bit  = 0  (Nx_Port) - This is the normal response to a N_Port Login request.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        574.96,
        540.16,
        586.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0038",
      "text": "The D_ID of the LS_ACC shall be the S_ID from the PLOGI.  The S_ID of the LS_ACC shall be",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        586.96,
        539.98,
        598.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0039",
      "text": "D_ID from the PLOGI.  The Payload shall include the Service Parameters for the destination",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        598.96,
        540.01,
        610.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0040",
      "text": "Nx_Port, a 64-bit N_Port_Name and a 64-bit Node_Name.  The N_Port Service Parameters",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        610.96,
        539.93,
        622.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0041",
      "text": "are as specified for in 6.6.  The applicability of the Service Parameters to N_Port Login are giv-",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        622.96,
        540.01,
        634.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0042",
      "text": "en in tables 150 and 155.  The Nx_Port may begin normal communication with the remote",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        634.96,
        538.9,
        646.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0043",
      "text": "N_Port.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        647.02,
        156.25,
        658.13
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 8,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0044",
      "text": "b) F_BSY with OX_ID equal to the OX_ID of the PLOGI.  The D_ID shall be the S_ID of the PLO-",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        671.02,
        539.91,
        682.13
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p158_s0045",
      "text": "GI.  The Fabric is busy.  The Nx_Port may retry the PLOGI again later. ",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        683.02,
        436.77,
        694.13
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    }
  ],
  "asset_ids": []
}